strings: <se_low>Chen Mui: That path only leads to my house.

<se_low>Chen Mui: Before we go there, I must find out
what happened to the Sanctuary.
We must speak with the Elders!
<voice_0x0100177F><se_low>*: Humans!? What are they doing here?
<voice_0x01001780><se_low>*: Grrr...! If only I had the strength to turn into my dragon form, I would scorch them where they stand!
<voice_0x01001781><se_low>Chen Mui: I should have expected that even ill health wouldn't quench your hatred of humans.
<voice_0x01001782><se_low>*: Master Chen Mui! So you brought these humans into our Sanctuary!?
<voice_0x01001783><se_low>*: You, you, you traitor! It's ridiculous notions like this that made your daughter commit her offence against our race!

<voice_0x01001784><se_low>Chen Mui: An offence against our race, you say?
You haven't changed one bit.
<voice_0x01001785><se_low>Chen Mui: Well. There's no sense trying to reason with a stone. Let's leave this stubborn old man to his own devices.
<voice_0x01001786><se_low>Chen Mui: Fool or not, it isn't right to antagonise a man on his sickbed.
